      <odd id="aspace_480a33378024bec64f51f3d6699b4fb0">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-B (YRG 38-B), Records documenting specific sports at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <altformavail id="aspace_5b8aaeb0821a04f951d5c2e446ea3c82">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>Basketball scrapbooks are available on microfilm from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no HM179. 1984-1985. 2348 frames on 4 reels, 35mm.</p>  
      </altformavail>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_076e726c3c389fbf85e097202f9c9f6e">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Department of Athletics, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_fce380578033cba7f58fcd12a23c8ab1">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are partially restricted. See inventory for details.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_888c9cc297acea254b17d329c691adb5">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Scrapbooks for the years 1915-1951 are available on microfilm. Patrons must use HM FILM 179 instead of the originals.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_e81fcbee5c3f8f09a1311b64294ee06b">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Department of Athletics, Yale University, Records Documenting Basketball (RU 947). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a1a1b842f906caa9c35f244a5f5d1500">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_7ea9c9fcafe6287475df89aa5990c8dd">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of scrapbooks, correspondence, scorecards, and reports documenting basketball at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
